  "texts": [
    "The data accumulated for a growing number of AGN indicate that the disc size varies as expected for the thin-disc model of Shakura and Sunyaev (1973).",
    "Uncertainties on the slope of the temperature profile are, however, still too large to robustly rule out alternatives.",
    "In addition, the disc size is found to be larger than predicted by the model (e.g.",
    "Edelson et al. 2015; Cackett et al. 2020; Guo et al. 2022).",
